---
title: Tex-Mex Pork Steak & Zesty Veggie Fries with Tomato Salad & Smokey Aioli
description: Eat the sunset with these colourful veggie fries, baked to crisp perfection. Tex-Mex spices on a pork steak continue those rich colours and flavours, dig in and enjoy feeling as warm as a sunset!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
